## ğŸ“Œ Project Objective

Predict the `tip` amount a customer will leave based on:

- Gender (`sex_encoded`)
- Smoking status (`smoker_encoded`)
- Day (`day_encoded`)
- Time (`time_encoded`)
- Group size (`size`)
- Total bill amount (`total_bill`)

